LABOR MARKETS:
• Levels.fyi compensation database
• LinkedIn Economic Graph salary insights
• Glassdoor salary reports by role and location
• Public company proxy statements (DEF 14A filings)
• Bureau of Labor Statistics occupational employment statistics

CAPITAL MARKETS:
• Bloomberg terminal for public company valuations
• Pitchbook for private company funding rounds
• CB Insights for venture capital trends
• SEC EDGAR for M&A transaction disclosures

MONETARY/COMMODITY MARKETS:
• World Gold Council quarterly demand reports
• COMEX gold futures and physical delivery data
• Federal Reserve H.4.1 reports (central bank holdings)
• IMF COFER database (currency composition of reserves)
• TIPS breakeven spreads for real yield calculations

TRADE FLOWS:
• US Census Bureau trade statistics
• UN Comtrade database
• Eurostat trade data
• National customs administrations

All tracking data will be compiled quarterly and published openly for independent 
verification and critique.

